nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=eAjuasjrUPQQ7kNvgENMx_y&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBRGnD9gd0_Uy0N2G6W4hI7l3K3vqV8qWj_fA73Evm9kA&oe=66F7F30E"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_49_22_19.Still025.png", "id": "1792607307852843", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035387_1792607311186176_5280458374548206595_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ntp5DKFBmigQ7kNvgHgvIxH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA-_moCpEnSrUeCjooWKNYLbPD6wXBMzAK_GMRGJXVtKA&oe=66F7F816"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_52_56_05.Still030.png", "id": "245249301718520", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031325_245249305051853_1598234300064219875_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0EwQrFfqojUQ7kNvgGiW8Us&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCwkE45L2Ep4hFYXxhK1gW7pKe3PkccKLKsRFFJhGI3dQ&oe=66F7D7B7"}, {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_11_37_00.Still002.png", "id": "733795254815172", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036675_733795258148505_1346935370172344005_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OcK5aE70DsMQ7kNvgFB8lhm&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCGP3cDsLCo5jUXtnP4pne1jgN9GGYt-YhQuK8_VEjfFA&oe=66F7DEF2"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Sequence 04.00_27_46_18.Still011.png", "id": "894248482404839", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974686_894248485738172_2991357501924730672_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0oV9FKvVFyAQ7kNvgH3uKiJ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDU-DjW3nL8KlIV9TA3NZ-GzFaL72cjNemU92Hp0iMQbw&oe=66F7F69B"}, "display_name": "FluentXR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Unlock a personalized language learning journey through your mixed reality home. FluentXR transforms your space into an interactive learning environment.\n\nStep into a realm where learning is not just fun and effective, but also deeply personalized. FluentXR is not just another language learning app; it's your own private linguistics lab.\n\nTag real-world objects in your space with text and audio labels, making learning immersive and contextually relevant. Dive into our Word Shuffle mini-game to reinforce your skills and challenge yourself using the timer.\n\nCurrent Features:\nSpace: Living Room\nMain Language: English\nLearning: French / fran\u00e7ais\nMini-Game: Word Shuffle\n470+ available tags geared towards common living room objects such as \u201cCouch\u201d, \u201cTelevision\u201d, \u201cChess Set\u201d and \u201cGaming Console\u201d\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, continually expanding its selection of languages, locations, and mini-games. Achieve language mastery with FluentXR\u2014where your home becomes your classroom.\n\nNext Expansion: \nSpace: Kitchen\nSpace: Bedroom\nMain Language: French\nLearning Language: Spanish / espa\u00f1ol \nLearning Language: English\nMini-Game: Sentence Scramble", "short_description": "Transform your language learning experience. \n\nUtilizing mixed-reality passthrough technology turn your home into a dynamic classroom. Tag real-world objects in your living room with 470+ customizable tags for learning French. Sharpen your skills through the Word Shuffle mini-game.\n\nFluentXR is an ever-evolving platform, updating with new languages, locations, and interactive mini-games. Dive into a context-rich home environment that's both captivating and practical."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zenfri.ca/fluentxr-privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "ZenFri Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://zenfri.ca/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recomme